        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 39–56. Pinnularia laterotundata sp. nov., Pinnularia perlanceolata sp. nov. and Pinnularia quesadae sp. nov. from Byers Peninsula. Figs 39–44. Pinnularia laterotundata sp. nov. Figs 39–44. LM of valves from specimens of type population. Figs 45–50. Pinnularia perlanceolata sp. nov. Figs 45–49. LM of valves from specimens of type population. Fig. 50. SEM of external view of entire valve. Figs 51–56. Pinnularia quesadae sp. nov. Figs 51–55. LM of valves from specimens of type population. Fig. 56. SEM of external view of entire valve. Scale bar = 10 µm, except Figs 50 & 56, scale bar = 5 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4894514/files/figure.png" .

